{"title":"内蒙古牧区民歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"内蒙古牧区民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高的山上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高的山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布谷鸟在歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧绿的草原上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊在自由成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝雾在山腰流动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们牧业社的包顶在山脚下闪光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多繁荣呵，我们的牧畜事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多美丽呵，我们的家乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑上马儿游牧呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊紧跟在我身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离家千里去游牧呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的牧业社在我心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广阔的草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广阔的草原上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边的羊群在移动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火般的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘扬在牧场的上空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的土地闪着金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年们狮子般投入劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线放出太阳的光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓舞着我们前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们满腔的热情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把钢铁熔化；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民伟大的事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀着我们对祖国的忠诚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（其木德道尔吉搜集，安谧吉译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}